    "guaranteed results",
    "from our database",
    "as discussed",
    "as we agreed",
    "per our conversation",
    "replace your team",
    "no human needed",
    "fully automated outreach",
    "we already work with",
    "act now or lose",
    "last chance",
    "limited time only",
    "100% guaranteed"
